                        "id": "5a96fda57fc8fb601adea285",
                        "uuid": "acc9f4b0-1233-4b65-93fb-6a7c6df807cf",
                        "title": "Cannot Select Multiple Files in Vista",
                        "slug": "cannot-select-multiple-files-in-vista",
                        "mobiledoc": "{\"version\":\"0.3.1\",\"markups\":[],\"atoms\":[],\"cards\":[[\"markdown\",{\"cardName\":\"card-markdown\",\"markdown\":\"I recently encountered this error on my friend's machine, had to search the net to find the solution but was worth the search, Here's how,\\r\\n<ol>\\r\\n\\t<li>Open <strong>Regedit</strong></li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Navigate to <strong>HKCU\\\\Software\\\\Classes\\\\Local Settings\\\\Software\\\\Microsoft\\\\Windows\\\\Shell\\\\</strong></li>\\r\\n\\t<li>Delete the <strong>Bags &amp; BagMRU</strong> keys</li>\\r\\n</ol>\\r\\nIf this does not help end the explorer.exe process and restart\"}]],\"sections\":[[10,0]],\"ghostVersion\":\"3.0\"}",
                        "html": "<!--kg-card-begin: markdown--><p>I recently encountered this error on my friend's machine, had to search the net to find the solution but was worth the search, Here's how,</p>\n<ol>\n\t<li>Open <strong>Regedit</strong></li>\n\t<li>Navigate to <strong>HKCU\\Software\\Classes\\Local Settings\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Shell\\</strong></li>\n\t<li>Delete the <strong>Bags &amp; BagMRU</strong> keys</li>\n</ol>\nIf this does not help end the explorer.exe process and restart<!--kg-card-end: markdown-->",
                        "comment_id": "51",
                        "plaintext": "I recently encountered this error on my friend's machine, had to search the net\nto find the solution but was worth the search, Here's how,\n\n 1. Open Regedit\n 2. Navigate to HKCU\\Software\\Classes\\Local\n    Settings\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Shell\\\n 3. Delete the Bags & BagMRU  keys\n\nIf this does not help end the explorer.exe process and restart",
