                        "slug": "asp-net-mvc-views-with-knockout",
                        "mobiledoc": "{\"version\":\"0.3.1\",\"markups\":[],\"atoms\":[],\"cards\":[[\"markdown\",{\"cardName\":\"card-markdown\",\"markdown\":\"We started moving sections of one of the apps that we are building to a SPA, while that is all and good, we could not migrate everything to JS+HTML all at once. So the idea was to do it in increments, So the Step 1 would be to move the list screens and bring in the collection.\\n\\n<script src=\\\"https://gist.github.com/nareshjois/7863567.js\\\"></script>\"}]],\"sections\":[[10,0]],\"ghostVersion\":\"3.0\"}",
                        "html": "<!--kg-card-begin: markdown--><p>We started moving sections of one of the apps that we are building to a SPA, while that is all and good, we could not migrate everything to JS+HTML all at once. So the idea was to do it in increments, So the Step 1 would be to move the list screens and bring in the collection.</p>\n<script src=\"https://gist.github.com/nareshjois/7863567.js\"></script><!--kg-card-end: markdown-->",
